<FONT color="#000000" size="6">*Icon Categories*</FONT>

To the left you see the icon categories you can choose between. _Click_ on the one you believe the icon you are looking for is in. You can then browse the icons sorted further into sub-categories, you can read the full descriptions and also search for icons based on tags.  Another way to find icons is by [http://code.google.com/p/google-maps-icons/downloads/list going to the Icon search page].
